Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sie-Sie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say you'll just be his second choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Saito-san has Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't lose to her charm at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your breasts and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love potion I confiscated from a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to use it on me of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things are illegal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it lasts only for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry, no one will find out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you shouldn't be so negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you're saying that, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say it's fair against an\Naristocrat unless you use a love potion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a charming glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control myself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't control people's hearts with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if it's just for a while, I can enjoy a dream, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, did you not go to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taking this water flea on probation for a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too harsh on Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare intervene in a matter between a familiar and his master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I am Saito-san's personal maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid is obliged to be concerned\Nabout her master's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you thinking much of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that if you can't trust your familiar, you don't love him enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were his master, I would take better care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you saying I'm doing it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it if you can. I'll watch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about for one month, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about one week?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped, then. I'll settle for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, make it one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel what it's like to be his owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start right away, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry now, or else we'll run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment ago Louise was dragging him around, and now it's Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fortunate, in a way, to get our parole with just weeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry! I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My delicate body isn't made for manual labour like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania! You can't give them any leeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Order of Pervert Knights who peeped at the girls' bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because my desire for ultimate beauty led me to the forbidden land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! Stop talking and keep working!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called us, the noble Order of Undine Knights, the Order of Pervert Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not really fine, but thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, what should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What", as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on time! We must make progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito-san, are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hesitate. Since today, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're playing newlyweds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Newlyweds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, since I want you to have some quality time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're a newlywed couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do newlyweds do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica! And Uncle Scarron, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came since we're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you use it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, about what I was saying before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the bride, and you're the husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's basically like playing house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So to start out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't breathing for a moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No! Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! I'll have dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that stupid maid and water flea disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally alone, Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, we're going to the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice and I go check the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to dodge your task just because I'm not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Jessica, you're so aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you two newlyweds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is the most basic of basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pushing it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tres bien! Maybe I'll put it into practice at our store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scare the customers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the time, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now. Your precious time is ticking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing it or are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made your point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Siesta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I'd get to see the\Nlegendary naked apron with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I die from divine retribution right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get any closer"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."and you're dead"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, going to toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the stimulation was too intense?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should just use the love potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Siesta, but I have to\Napologise to her and return to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really return?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might never get this kind of chance ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's holding you back, Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and put this in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Saito-san will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control myself anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's what your "good care" is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this are first come, first served!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever takes the step wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win in bust size, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it about busts, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love potion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Montmorency. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I breathed in the potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you're amazingly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making my heart throb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I said you're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heartless words are so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you're a girl and so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stay still, I'll rip your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha! Help me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help with scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other matters are not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't touch there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! You really can't touch there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how much you've grown since we last met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! Absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That love potion is starting a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... about that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I gave to Siesta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do something before this gets any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me touch your fine bosom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're done, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha... When I take a good look at you, your small and thin body's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see how small yours are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it taste good, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of noisy outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not worry about the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, please look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that I'm Princess Guldenhorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as tough as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency-neesama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It spreads through kisses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This strange feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Something looks strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how long should I keep an eye on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Tiffania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful white skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll suffocate others with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to punish you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! Don't take her all for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch them, too! I want to kiss her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Scarron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a manly maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so different from a skinny stuck-up I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it feels like to be hugged by those arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Saito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Mi mademoiselle".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! I said you're making me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My crotch... My crotch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My balls...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming after my breasts and hugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's a magic that makes people lose their senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of here, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa. So that's where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quarrel between us started the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll end it using our bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your bodies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make love just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined the effects of the\Nlove potion would spread this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to use it at a place like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{spell}Nau cid yisa waysarel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{spell}Hagaraz yul beog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{spell}Need is algees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{spell}Bel kana man lagoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was having a great dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't be here! Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, what was that magic you just used?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I think the love potion I had caused this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real low quality one, but it was yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I don't remember anything, and I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not play a prank like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic for oblivion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's the only spell I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It erases memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of such magic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chevalier de Norfatul, Tabitha-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here and not in Gallia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master wants a dragon, of which only four exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I'm talking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you're very familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. This could be a chance for you to regain your mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Succeed in your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror, oh mirror, tell me! Who do I want to be the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll be someone unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sleipnir Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, come find me quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
